Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As times change, difficult\Ncases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is alibi destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use someone and you'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single\Ntruth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:50.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Akaoni Fire Festival Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are we going\Nto find any clues
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about those men in black?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that if I made\Nold man Mori famous
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'd get more clients and then\Nmaybe we'd find out about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got more clients, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but we haven't heard\Nanything about those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Act hastily and they\Nmight find out about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might put Ran and\Nthe old man in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait quietly for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective needs\Npatience too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what kind\Nof experiment is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? It's a--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you know what kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A dangerous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lousy situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's old man Mori. What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent choice, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have your address, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! I'm working!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you following\Nthat guy around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!\NWhat if he notices me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go tell Ran I won't\Nbe home for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:08.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Akaoni Village Fire Festival\NSunday, November 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about an easy job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half a million yen just for\Nwatching someone for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some jobs really\Nrake in the dough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because everyone\Nadmires your great detective work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm amazed at how\NI've solved one case after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I solved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nyour job's been going well
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} came!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he brought\Nsome good luck with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. How long are we gonna\Ntake care of this twerp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are his parents\Nstill in the hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, when I visited\NProfessor Agasa yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did get out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then they suddenly\Ngot transferred overseas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They left yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? They just left\NConan-{\i1}kun {\i0}behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they'll send\Nfor him once they settle in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're taking\Ncare of him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has nowhere else to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, you've been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever talk to his parents, I'll have\Nto charge them for his upbringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 8:00 pm today,\Na man's body was found
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the burning tower\Nof the Akaoni Fire Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to his personal effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the body was that of\N42 year old Negishi Masaki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--are investigating this\Nas a possible murder--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Dad?\NDid you know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just that;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with him\Nfor three whole days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He's the guy\NI followed around until yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Negishi Masaki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad sure is taking a long time\Nto give his statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to be expected--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was with the\Nguy up until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police don't get\Nmany witnesses like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of case is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, old man!\NI can't wait to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half a billion yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The late Negishi-{\i1}san\N{\i0}had a life insurance policy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,worth half a billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it seem strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he give\Nall that insurance money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to an ordinary friend like you,\NAbe Yutaka-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the one\Nwho hired me to trail him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he give you\Nthe insurance money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had been friends\Nsince college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we went\Ndrinking one day, he--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not young anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna bet on who lives the longest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does half a billion yen sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I accepted his invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you both took out\N500-million yen policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea the bet would\Nlast only three months...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you\Nhave Mori-{\i1}kun {\i0}trail him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No big reason, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He recently told me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he thought someone\Nwas out to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out to kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was joking at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he wasn't acting quite normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I had Mori-{\i1}san\N{\i0}watch him for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I run a small business,\Nso I'm actually quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please find Negishi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Nkiller as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you the instant we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only one\NI can see as the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he has an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An airtight one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's fishy!\NHe's definitely the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half a million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to follow a guy for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his confident attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too fond of that, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why can't they arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His alibi is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was the one\Nwho verified it for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body was found on Sunday night,\Nduring the Fire Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on his tail the entire time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nthe crime took place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between late Saturday\Nnight and Sunday evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the flame tower was lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the person you suspect\Nmust've done it during then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was on a company trip to Kyushu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Saturday morning\Nuntil this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are\Nyou so fixated on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My detective's intuition...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His alibi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One Week Later
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn Abe got\NNegishi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s insurance money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got the half-billion\Nyen just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to destroy\Nhis alibi, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The schedule and\Npictures of his Kyushu trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Inspector Megure\Nto let me borrow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a clue\Nin one of these photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch!\NI, the great Mori Kogoro-{\i1}sama{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will expose his trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just hope\Nhe doesn't burn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Dad, couldn't he have come back\Non short notice on a domestic flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's very possible.\NBut his alibi has no holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially during the\Ntime the murder occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He played mahjong with his\Nemployees all Saturday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunday afternoon,\Nhe toured the city on bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has pictures to prove it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only time he was alone was when\Nhe took a two hour nap Sunday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be impossible to go to\NGunma and back in that amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These photos are weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's by a clock in every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must really like clocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like he took\Nthese to prove his alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the kid's right--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like whenever\NI'm stuck on something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll say something\Nthat gives me a hint...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in this envelope?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those are--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--from when I followed the guy--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh! They're mixed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who got killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he give you a boo-boo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he is just a stupid kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are you sure this\Nis the guy who was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body was all burned up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was definitely him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His driver's license\Nwas lying right next
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the flame tower at the fire festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teeth even\Nmatched his dental records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Criminals normally hide their crimes;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's far too intentional for the\Nbody to be hidden under the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and an easily-understood\Nclue to be lying nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one person stood to\Ngain from the body's discovery:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abe, who would get\Nthe insurance money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's right--\Nhe's the only possible person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he has an airtight alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there has to be something\Nthat will destroy his story!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This photograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.\NThe Negishi-{\i1}san {\i0}I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was right-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are from\NThursday and Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these are from Saturday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man followed Negishi-{\i1}san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Thursday to Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body was found on Sunday night,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the murder took place between\NSaturday night and Sunday evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Abe Yutaka was in Kyushu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Saturday morning\Nuntil Monday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His alibi is flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if my theory is correct,\Nthen it's actually--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business, twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look away for a second\Nand he causes trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hit Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}just\Nbecause you can't solve the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abe Yutaka is\Nclearly responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even has a motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His business was\N300 million yen in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used the insurance\Nmoney to pay it off
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and plans to escape\Noverseas with the rest of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overseas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left someone in charge of the company,\Nsaying that he was going on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his plane\Nleaves at 9:00 tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,9:00?! That leaves\Nus only three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let him leave the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only chance now is to corner\Nhim and make him confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time! First, I need\Nto get them to the airport!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll use that method!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You destroyed\NAbe's alibi, Inspector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm on my way to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent! I'll see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, now to use\Nthe old man's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Inspector Megure!\NThis is Mori Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,New Tokyo International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come every single time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just finding the Inspector\Nis going to be tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which flight is Abe's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! They're about\Nto start boarding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous,\Nbut I'll have to lure him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paging Abe Yutaka-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Nbound for Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on Flight Number 99...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Negishi Masaki-{\i1}sama {\i0}is waiting\Nfor you in the main parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, Abe Yutaka-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Nbound for Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on Flight Number 99--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! How did you\Ndestroy Abe's alibi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you found out how.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where did Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was clever of you, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negishi-{\i1}san {\i0}actually died\NFriday night, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The day before\Nyou left on your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you had Detective Mori follow a\Nfake Negishi-{\i1}san {\i0}around the following day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to make us think\Nhe was alive until Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You checked the date of the festival\Nin advance, and just as you planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his body was found\Non Sunday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his precise time\Nof death indeterminable,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Mori's statement put it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between Saturday night\Nand Sunday evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you returned Monday afternoon,\Nas if nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, your alibi was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the policemen\Ntalking about the case
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I tried applying\Nmy own kind of logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mistake was the substitute\Nyou chose for Negishi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might've fooled the detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no fooling the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your actor was left-handed,\Nunlike Negishi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give yourself up. This place\Nis crawling with police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Abe Yutaka, was indeed\NNegishi Masaki's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't be turning myself in.\NI'm going to live it up overseas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? But I'll tell everyone\Nthat you confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody'll believe you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they might believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Abe Yutaka, was indeed\NNegishi Masaki's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to have your business\Non the verge of bankruptcy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got what he deserved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was stupid enough to take out\Nsuch a huge insurance policy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had no idea I'd kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were stupid\Nenough to let me kill you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the stupid one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna let you off\Neasy if you turned yourself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you've gone too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smash in that\Nrotten head of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Abe Yutaka, was indeed\NNegishi Masaki's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one lousy bastard\Nto use me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they found\Nthe fake Negishi-{\i1}san {\i0}too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Apparently Abe asked him\Nto wander around all day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for no specific reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bothers me is what\NAbe said afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the kid! He did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only kid around then was--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't easy being a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Ran is alone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.32,0:24:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like these might\Nbe random murders...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.53,0:24:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Wealthy Daughter\NMurder Case (Part 1)."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.74,0:24:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.99,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.47,0:24:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is finally Part 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.35,0:24:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-chan's in danger again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.43,0:24:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.68,0:24:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
